text: Jar-Kyshtak may refer to the following places in Kyrgyzstan: *Jar-Kyshtak, Barpy, a village in Barpy rural community, Suzak District, Jalal-Abad Region *Jar-Kyshtak, Yrys, a village in Yrys rural community, Suzak District, Jalal- Abad Region *Jar-Kyshtak, Osh, a village in Alay District, Osh Region
title: Jar-Kyshtak
